WEBVTT

00:00:04.714 --> 00:00:09.885
Is the destiny of mankind controlled
by some transcendental entity or Law?

00:00:10.761 --> 00:00:13.806
Is it like the hand of
God hovering above?

00:00:14.807 --> 00:00:16.642
At least it is true...

00:00:17.143 --> 00:00:20.771
...that man has no
control, even over his own will.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:00:52.219 --> 00:00:53.971
What is this?

00:00:58.100 --> 00:00:59.351
Why?

00:00:59.810 --> 00:01:02.605
Why are we here?

00:01:23.709 --> 00:01:25.711
<i>Feel no shame about shape.</i>

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:27.671
<i>Weather changes the phrase.</i>

00:01:27.838 --> 00:01:31.342
<i>Even mother will
show you another way.</i>

00:01:31.675 --> 00:01:33.803
<i>So, put your glasses on.</i>

00:01:33.928 --> 00:01:35.846
<i>Nothing will be wrong.</i>

00:01:35.971 --> 00:01:38.099
<i>There's no blame, there's no fame.</i>

00:01:38.307 --> 00:01:39.934
<i>It's up to you.</i>

00:01:40.101 --> 00:01:43.604
<i>The first words should be found.</i>

00:01:44.230 --> 00:01:47.191
<i>Whatever holds you back.</i>

00:01:47.983 --> 00:01:48.609
<i>I...</i>

00:01:48.984 --> 00:01:49.693
<i>... can...</i>

00:01:49.819 --> 00:01:51.862
<i>I can get it off.</i>

00:01:51.987 --> 00:01:52.947
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:53.114 --> 00:01:53.864
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:53.989 --> 00:01:55.741
<i>Tell me what you want.</i>

00:01:55.866 --> 00:01:56.867
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:57.076 --> 00:01:57.827
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:57.993 --> 00:01:59.745
<i>I don't know why you are afraid.</i>

00:01:59.995 --> 00:02:00.955
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:02:01.122 --> 00:02:01.872
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:02:02.123 --> 00:02:03.582
<i>Tell me what you'd say.</i>

00:02:03.874 --> 00:02:04.875
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:02:05.084 --> 00:02:06.001
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:02:06.127 --> 00:02:06.752
<i>Too late...</i>

00:02:06.961 --> 00:02:08.420
<i>It's too late.</i>

00:02:13.634 --> 00:02:17.638
Time of Eternity

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:25.563
The symbol that has
been branded on to your skin...

00:02:25.688 --> 00:02:27.148
...marks you as sacrificial offerings.

00:02:27.398 --> 00:02:30.192
The life of those who have
been branded now belong to us...

00:02:30.317 --> 00:02:34.280
...as offerings, and
every last drop of your blood...

00:02:34.822 --> 00:02:36.323
...until your death throes...

00:02:36.532 --> 00:02:39.702
...is food for the life of our
beloved unborn child of darkness.

00:02:40.452 --> 00:02:41.412
Wait!

00:02:42.288 --> 00:02:43.789
Hang on, Griffith!

00:02:44.665 --> 00:02:47.459
I'll get you out of there soon!

00:02:48.169 --> 00:02:49.295
It's no use!

00:02:49.420 --> 00:02:51.964
Human strength is
utterly useless in this case.

00:02:52.214 --> 00:02:55.342
Your help is irrelevant in this matter.

00:02:55.467 --> 00:02:57.344
All is dictated by his own will.

00:02:57.845 --> 00:02:58.721
Shut up!

00:02:59.471 --> 00:03:01.348
You must have heard what we said...

00:03:01.724 --> 00:03:03.434
He's the one who has the final say.

00:03:03.684 --> 00:03:04.727
I said...

00:03:04.852 --> 00:03:05.978
Shut up!

00:03:09.857 --> 00:03:12.610
That's not possible!

00:03:34.381 --> 00:03:35.257
Was it you...

00:03:36.258 --> 00:03:37.968
Was it you who wanted this?

00:03:46.769 --> 00:03:51.398
Sacrifice, sacrifice, sacrifice...

00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:22.471
Pippin!

00:04:22.846 --> 00:04:23.639
Run!

00:04:27.268 --> 00:04:28.018
Go!

00:04:28.269 --> 00:04:29.520
Run, run away!

00:04:29.645 --> 00:04:31.146
Survive and live on!

00:04:31.730 --> 00:04:32.606
What are you saying!

00:04:35.901 --> 00:04:36.986
What are you doing?

00:04:37.111 --> 00:04:38.404
Let go, Pippin is...

00:04:43.993 --> 00:04:44.785
Pippin!

00:04:45.119 --> 00:04:47.037
We can't leave him there to die!

00:04:47.413 --> 00:04:48.289
Stop it!

00:04:48.872 --> 00:04:51.125
You are our leader now!

00:04:51.500 --> 00:04:52.626
You must survive!

00:04:52.793 --> 00:04:55.296
As long as we have a commander,
it's not the end of the Hawks.

00:04:55.796 --> 00:04:59.925
I won't let us end this way, not like this!

00:05:18.944 --> 00:05:21.196
Commander!

00:06:03.989 --> 00:06:05.115
A dream.

00:06:05.741 --> 00:06:08.077
This is all a dream!

00:06:09.745 --> 00:06:10.996
The Midland Army...

00:06:11.330 --> 00:06:12.831
The Band of Hawk...

00:06:12.998 --> 00:06:15.000
It was all a dream!

00:06:16.001 --> 00:06:21.632
If you think about it, it was
all much too good to be true...

00:06:22.257 --> 00:06:24.635
That's right!

00:06:24.885 --> 00:06:26.512
All a dream!

00:06:27.388 --> 00:06:30.140
This is all a dream!

00:06:30.349 --> 00:06:33.018
When I open my eyes,
everything will be over!

00:06:45.906 --> 00:06:46.865
And all I'll have is myself.

00:06:47.157 --> 00:06:48.992
A woman in hell?

00:06:49.243 --> 00:06:50.911
This must be a dream.

00:06:53.122 --> 00:06:54.415
Damn it.

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:56.917
I'm such a sucker.

00:06:57.668 --> 00:06:59.545
Why?

00:07:03.173 --> 00:07:04.508
Damn it.

00:07:15.394 --> 00:07:16.562
Judeau, to your right!

00:07:20.774 --> 00:07:21.567
Judeau!

00:07:25.946 --> 00:07:26.905
Are you all right?

00:07:27.322 --> 00:07:29.908
Yeah, you saved me.

00:07:31.952 --> 00:07:32.786
Judeau...

00:07:34.455 --> 00:07:35.539
That's enough...

00:07:35.664 --> 00:07:36.582
Turn back!

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.709
It's the same, wherever we go!

00:07:38.834 --> 00:07:40.043
They'll come after us!

00:07:41.086 --> 00:07:44.965
We should at least end it
together with our swords in our hands.

00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:46.842
Quiet, you'll bite your tongue!

00:07:48.218 --> 00:07:49.553
We've got to fight it.

00:07:49.845 --> 00:07:53.474
We'll struggle and
resist, right to the bitter end.

00:07:54.725 --> 00:07:57.352
You want to face
them just to get killed?

00:07:58.228 --> 00:08:00.105
No thanks, I don't want that.

00:08:00.189 --> 00:08:01.231
Guts wouldn't either.

00:08:09.072 --> 00:08:09.865
Judeau!

00:08:18.749 --> 00:08:19.500
Judeau!

00:08:23.128 --> 00:08:24.129
Move, stupid!

00:08:28.342 --> 00:08:29.259
Why are you...

00:08:30.260 --> 00:08:31.345
That's enough.

00:08:31.970 --> 00:08:33.180
Stop!

00:08:54.701 --> 00:08:55.452
Judeau!

00:08:56.453 --> 00:08:57.704
Did I get him?

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:00.666
With my last knife?

00:09:00.791 --> 00:09:02.084
Yes, you got him.

00:09:02.209 --> 00:09:03.043
He's dead.

00:09:04.336 --> 00:09:05.337
Go...

00:09:05.671 --> 00:09:07.047
What the hell are you saying?

00:09:07.172 --> 00:09:10.175
You just said we have to
struggle, resist until the very end!

00:09:10.592 --> 00:09:11.468
Stand UP!

00:09:11.802 --> 00:09:13.720
I'm taking you with me,
even if I have to drag you!

00:09:15.681 --> 00:09:17.224
All right...

00:09:17.599 --> 00:09:19.184
I obey.

00:09:19.309 --> 00:09:20.602
Even if it means crawling...

00:09:20.727 --> 00:09:22.854
Yes, you'd better!

00:09:23.438 --> 00:09:26.233
I guess I wasn't thinking
carefully when I said all that...

00:09:26.358 --> 00:09:28.819
Take responsibility for your own words.

00:09:29.111 --> 00:09:31.613
I'm afraid I've always
been, you know, all talk.

00:09:31.738 --> 00:09:33.865
If you've got the strength for excuses...

00:09:33.865 --> 00:09:35.117
...use it to walk!

00:09:35.826 --> 00:09:39.871
So many things I wanted to share...

00:09:40.122 --> 00:09:42.124
...I guess I missed my chance.

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.627
Those few important words...

00:09:48.505 --> 00:09:51.883
You sure do cry a lot, don't you?

00:09:53.510 --> 00:09:57.347
I guess these are my last words.

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:04.771
Judeau?

00:10:42.768 --> 00:10:43.685
The sacrifice...

00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:45.270
Sacrifice...

00:10:45.437 --> 00:10:47.064
The sacrificial woman...

00:10:48.565 --> 00:10:50.317
The sacrificial woman...

00:10:52.402 --> 00:10:53.820
Shall we eat?

00:10:53.945 --> 00:10:55.781
Shall we eat now?

00:10:56.448 --> 00:10:58.700
But before that...

00:10:59.201 --> 00:11:01.078
Before that...

00:11:02.079 --> 00:11:02.954
Guts!

00:11:28.980 --> 00:11:31.191
The boy really does
try hard, doesn't he?

00:11:35.195 --> 00:11:36.488
Isn't it ironic?

00:11:36.697 --> 00:11:39.741
The more powerful his vitality is...

00:11:40.117 --> 00:11:42.994
...and the longer he
draws out this struggle...

00:11:43.495 --> 00:11:47.708
...the more precious will he be for
the one born in this darkness to feed on.

00:11:48.375 --> 00:11:50.627
Sweet dreams to
you, our infant apostle.

00:11:52.754 --> 00:11:55.507
Your entire being is
built upon Griffith's dream.

00:11:57.884 --> 00:11:59.886
When his dream is over...

00:12:00.011 --> 00:12:02.013
...you will finally open your eyes...

00:12:02.514 --> 00:12:05.142
...within this dream that never ends.

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:14.234
Where...

00:12:15.527 --> 00:12:16.903
Where am I?

00:12:18.155 --> 00:12:19.531
I feel my body...

00:12:20.907 --> 00:12:22.409
...sinking...

00:12:23.994 --> 00:12:25.036
...deep...

00:12:59.446 --> 00:13:03.200
Their deaths pierce through me.

00:13:06.328 --> 00:13:07.704
The men I killed...

00:13:08.830 --> 00:13:10.457
Because of my desires...

00:13:11.833 --> 00:13:12.959
How strange...

00:13:13.585 --> 00:13:14.961
I don't feel a thing...

00:13:16.922 --> 00:13:18.465
Just sinking...

00:13:24.346 --> 00:13:25.472
What's this?

00:13:26.097 --> 00:13:29.726
The last tear drop you cried.

00:13:34.189 --> 00:13:38.985
When a person faces suffering
so great that it can tear them in two...

00:13:39.361 --> 00:13:41.112
...their heart freezes.

00:13:45.242 --> 00:13:46.368
Behelits?

00:13:46.993 --> 00:13:48.954
These are just splashes...

00:13:49.746 --> 00:13:52.999
Splashes off waves in
the ocean of the other world...

00:13:53.333 --> 00:13:55.210
A droplet of the future...

00:13:55.836 --> 00:13:58.004
A calling from the other side.

00:14:30.537 --> 00:14:31.371
Blood!

00:14:40.797 --> 00:14:42.549
Isn't anyone alive?

00:14:43.174 --> 00:14:44.009
Judeau!

00:14:44.384 --> 00:14:45.260
Pippin!

00:14:45.886 --> 00:14:46.803
Corkus!

00:14:49.431 --> 00:14:50.891
Caska...

00:14:52.058 --> 00:14:53.393
Commander...

00:14:56.688 --> 00:14:57.564
Gaston!

00:14:57.939 --> 00:14:59.274
You're alive!

00:15:02.068 --> 00:15:05.030
Well, I hardly feel like I'm alive anymore.

00:15:05.405 --> 00:15:06.823
Where's the rest of the group?

00:15:06.948 --> 00:15:08.199
Who else is alive?

00:15:08.700 --> 00:15:10.076
I don't know.

00:15:10.452 --> 00:15:12.829
I was running like
hell trying to get away.

00:15:13.455 --> 00:15:15.916
After a while I realized
what kind of condition I was in.

00:15:16.541 --> 00:15:19.711
I don't know what
happened to the rest of them.

00:15:21.463 --> 00:15:22.714
Commander.

00:15:23.298 --> 00:15:25.175
What do you think this means?

00:15:25.967 --> 00:15:28.345
It's as if we're in a bad dream.

00:15:31.222 --> 00:15:31.848
Gaston!

00:15:47.489 --> 00:15:48.239
Pippin!

00:15:48.740 --> 00:15:49.991
You're alive!

00:15:50.992 --> 00:15:51.952
Pippin!

00:16:31.032 --> 00:16:33.159
You bastards!

00:16:34.869 --> 00:16:37.247
You bastards!

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:37.307
It is the birth...

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:39.559
...of our fifth blessed King...

00:17:39.684 --> 00:17:42.062
Our demon prince...

00:17:43.188 --> 00:17:44.773
You are an extension of us...

00:17:45.190 --> 00:17:48.568
Our latest kinsman
to wear the crown of evil.

00:17:49.569 --> 00:17:51.571
The Wings of Darkness...

00:17:51.696 --> 00:17:52.906
Femto!

00:18:23.103 --> 00:18:24.854
Griffith?

00:18:53.633 --> 00:18:55.009
Griffith?

00:19:53.193 --> 00:19:54.569
Griffith!

00:20:16.174 --> 00:20:17.550
Oh, it's beautiful...

00:20:17.717 --> 00:20:19.344
How it moves me...

00:20:20.595 --> 00:20:24.974
Love, hatred, torment, pleasure...

00:20:25.225 --> 00:20:27.060
Life and death...

00:20:27.602 --> 00:20:29.604
All together before our eyes...

00:20:29.979 --> 00:20:31.606
This is the beauty of man...

00:20:31.940 --> 00:20:33.608
...and the devil

00:21:21.030 --> 00:21:23.241
<i>Looking back, the morning comes.</i>

00:21:23.366 --> 00:21:26.869
<i>Don't find your face in your glass.</i>

00:21:28.037 --> 00:21:30.915
<i>Take the moonlight by the tail.</i>

00:21:31.040 --> 00:21:33.876
<i>It's a rainy sight that you're shading.</i>

00:21:35.545 --> 00:21:37.130
<i>What is that?</i>

00:21:37.255 --> 00:21:38.423
<i>It's just the same.</i>

00:21:38.548 --> 00:21:41.551
<i>What is trying on your crown?</i>

00:21:42.802 --> 00:21:45.680
<i>I'm spending my
glass and walking back.</i>

00:21:45.888 --> 00:21:49.058
<i>So wear my glass, you're fading.</i>

00:21:49.434 --> 00:21:52.687
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:21:53.146 --> 00:21:56.065
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:21:56.774 --> 00:21:59.777
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:00.653 --> 00:22:03.448
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:04.324 --> 00:22:07.910
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:08.161 --> 00:22:10.288
<i>I'm waiting...</i>

00:22:38.691 --> 00:22:39.984
You going?

00:22:42.362 --> 00:22:44.238
Don't get yourself killed.

00:22:45.305 --> 00:23:45.404
